      "raw_text": "PORTLAND, Ore, Oct. Sat the\nannual convention of the Northwest\nFruitgrowers' association. to be held\nin Portland In January, a proposition\nto organize an association of fruit\nraisers of the Inland Empire will\nprobably come up The project would\ninclude the Walla Walla, Snake River,\nLewiston, Yakima. Wenatchee and\none or two other districts. and the OBJ\nject to advance the interests of fruit\nmen In common, such as adjustment\nof obnoxious freight rates and max\ning common cause against fruit tree\npests. The organization of California\nfruitgrowers would be the one prob\nably used as n model."
